Dark Cloud (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dark_Cloud_(actor) 0 Dark Cloud (1855–1918) was a First Nations silent film actor, born Elijah Tahamont. He was a chief of the Abenaki, a First Nations band government belonging to the Algonquin people of northeastern North America.
